  "texts": [
    "This disparity is possible because the topic is relatively new or the scarce presence of artificial intelligence laboratories focused on applications related to higher education in regions where such publications have not been recorded.",
    "The results highlight the global importance of research on the application of generative artificial intelligence in higher education.",
    "However, it is crucial to recognize that the choice of database could have significantly influenced the observed geographic distribution.",
    "Regarding the approach or type of research in the studies reviewed, it is observed that 57.14% of them adopt a quantitative approach, while 17.85% adhere to a qualitative approach.",
    "On the other hand, the mixed approach contributes 25.00% of the total."
  ]
}